     "text": [
      "Atlas directory: /neurodesktop-storage/aphasia-lesion-pipeline/atlases\n",
      "  ℹ Re-using 4 atlas(es) already loaded in this kernel session.\n",
      "• HarvardOxford: cached (49 regions)\n",
      "• AAL: cached (5 regions)\n",
      "• Destrieux: cached (151 regions)\n",
      "• Schaefer400: cached (401 regions)\n",
