y)</b> <small style='color:#aaa;font-size:10px'>(fluency)</small></td><td style='padding:4px 8px'><span title='raw score = +0.60' style='color:#f0a500;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px'>&#9733;</span> <small style='color:#666'>weak / preliminary</small></td><td style='text-align:center;padding:4px 4px'>2</td><td style='font-size:11px;color:#666;padding:4px 4px'>@Alyahya2018NounVerb</td></tr><tr><td style='padding:4px 2px'><span style=\"background:#6c757d;color:white;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:3px;font-size:11px\">AMBIGUOUS</span></td><td style='padding:4px 8px'><small style='color:#888;font-size:10px'>[impairment]</small> <b>Phonological production</b> <small style='color:#aaa;font-size:10px'>(phonological_production)</small></td><td style='padding:4px 8px'><span title='raw score = +0.00' style='color:#f0a500;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px'>&#8212;</span> <small style='color:#666'>no net evidence</small></td><td style='text-align:center;padding:4px 4px'>2</td><td style='font-size:11px;color:#666;padding:4px 4px'>@Alyahya2018NounVerb</td></tr></table>\n",
